1
00:01:12,948 --> 00:01:13,783
Tim Putih?

2
00:01:15,451 --> 00:01:16,744
SATU JAM LALU

3
00:01:16,827 --> 00:01:19,830
Aku mundur dari jabatanku
sebagai pemimpin Tim Putih.

4
00:01:20,581 --> 00:01:21,499
Kau mundur?

5
00:01:23,709 --> 00:01:24,752
Ya.

6
00:01:24,835 --> 00:01:28,005
Lututku sakit setelah menebang pohon,

7
00:01:28,506 --> 00:01:30,341
jadi, nenek Dong-pyo menggantikanku.

8
00:01:30,424 --> 00:01:32,593
Mungkin tak kelihatan,

9
00:01:32,676 --> 00:01:36,680
tetapi di tahun 1967,
aku pernah ikut tim estafet SD Shinsu.

10
00:01:37,306 --> 00:01:40,184
Waktu itu aku hampir lolos
ke Festival Olahraga Nasional.

11
00:01:40,267 --> 00:01:42,144
Tenang saja.

12
00:01:42,686 --> 00:01:43,687
Tahun 1967?

13
00:01:44,480 --> 00:01:45,648
Saat usia 12 tahun.

14
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,568
Begitu.

15
00:01:54,532 --> 00:01:57,326
30 MENIT LALU

16
00:01:58,953 --> 00:02:02,289
Ini saatnya menggunakan
keterampilan Pembantai Cerita-ku.

17
00:02:05,292 --> 00:02:09,338
Pak Hong, apa keadilan bagimu?

18
00:02:10,339 --> 00:02:11,173
Keadilan?

19
00:02:12,550 --> 00:02:13,759
"Keadilan".

20
00:02:13,843 --> 00:02:16,637
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">"Fiat justitia ruat caelum."</font></i>

21
00:02:17,263 --> 00:02:19,682
{\an8}"Tegakkan keadilan meski langit runtuh."

22
00:02:19,765 --> 00:02:21,225
{\an8}Itu kata Kant.

23
00:02:21,308 --> 00:02:25,563
{\an8}Dengan kata lain,
aturan tak dipatuhi berdasarkan situasi,

24
00:02:25,646 --> 00:02:27,690
{\an8}tetapi harus dijalankan

25
00:02:27,773 --> 00:02:29,775
{\an8}betapa pun buruk konsekuensinya.

26
00:02:29,859 --> 00:02:33,070
{\an8}Aku memilih bola putih ini
di hadapan para siswa.

27
00:02:33,153 --> 00:02:36,615
{\an8}Namun, jika hasil ini diubah
karena itu merugikan timmu?

28
00:02:36,699 --> 00:02:39,660
{\an8}Itu melanggar aturan
yang kita buat sendiri.

29
00:02:41,245 --> 00:02:42,121
{\an8}Wah.

30
00:02:44,081 --> 00:02:45,374
{\an8}Kau secerdas ini?

31
00:02:45,457 --> 00:02:48,836
{\an8}Kau selalu tutup mulut,
mana mungkin aku tahu?

32
00:02:49,587 --> 00:02:52,256
{\an8}Kau pandai bicara.

33
00:02:52,756 --> 00:02:55,801
{\an8}Kalau begitu, langsung saja ke intinya.

34
00:02:56,969 --> 00:02:58,053
Aku, Yoon Bom,

35
00:02:58,804 --> 00:03:00,389
akan tetap di Tim Putih.

36
00:03:01,307 --> 00:03:05,185
Keputusan ini hanya untuk satu alasan.

37
00:03:05,269 --> 00:03:07,187
Sebagai guru etika,

38
00:03:07,271 --> 00:03:09,857
aku harus menunjukkan keadilan
kepada siswa…

39
00:03:10,441 --> 00:03:12,151
Ya, silakan saja.

40
00:03:15,988 --> 00:03:16,822
Maaf?

41
00:03:17,448 --> 00:03:18,866
Terserah kau saja.

42
00:03:27,207 --> 00:03:29,960
Tim Putih, kalian siap menang?

43
00:03:30,044 --> 00:03:30,878
Semangat!

44
00:03:30,961 --> 00:03:32,796
-Semangat!
-Semangat!

45
00:03:38,427 --> 00:03:40,137
Hei, Sun Han-gyul.

46
00:03:42,806 --> 00:03:44,975
Apa kau membohongiku?

47
00:03:45,726 --> 00:03:46,727
Tidak.

48
00:03:47,353 --> 00:03:49,688
Kata Se-jin, Bu Bom di Tim Biru.

49
00:03:49,772 --> 00:03:51,023
Kita mulai.

50
00:03:51,106 --> 00:03:53,108
-Semangat, Tim Putih!
-Betul!

51
00:03:53,192 --> 00:03:54,652
-Semangat!
-Semangat!

52
00:03:54,735 --> 00:03:55,653
Semangat.

53
00:04:00,491 --> 00:04:01,617
Apa yang terjadi?

54
00:04:01,700 --> 00:04:03,911
Bukankah gurumu ada di Tim Biru?

55
00:04:05,079 --> 00:04:07,873
Siapa peduli dia Tim Biru atau Putih?

56
00:04:08,457 --> 00:04:10,626
Kakak hanya harus peduli satu hal,

57
00:04:10,709 --> 00:04:11,794
yaitu aku. Mengerti?

58
00:04:13,003 --> 00:04:15,589
Kukira kalian berdua di Tim Biru.

59
00:04:15,673 --> 00:04:18,801
Jadi, aku bekerja keras
agar kalian menang.

60
00:04:19,593 --> 00:04:20,636
-Tidak.
-Pemanasan.

61
00:04:20,719 --> 00:04:22,888
Aku ingin dia kalah.

62
00:04:23,389 --> 00:04:24,223
Tanganmu juga.

63
00:04:24,932 --> 00:04:26,308
-Hati-hati.
-Kakak tahu

64
00:04:26,392 --> 00:04:28,644
kenapa dia pindah dari Seoul ke sini?

65
00:04:29,353 --> 00:04:30,437
Kau tahu dari mana?

66
00:04:31,146 --> 00:04:33,440
Apa ini? Kakak tahu dari mana?

67
00:04:34,274 --> 00:04:35,776
Apa Ayah memberitahumu?

68
00:04:35,859 --> 00:04:38,320
Aku minta Sekretaris Jung mencari tahu.

69
00:04:38,404 --> 00:04:42,324
Ternyata ada alasan kenapa guru Se-jin
datang kemari dari Seoul.

70
00:04:42,408 --> 00:04:44,034
Apa alasannya?

71
00:04:44,118 --> 00:04:47,162
Tampaknya ada masalah dengan pria.

72
00:04:47,246 --> 00:04:48,914
Apa? Ada-ada saja.

73
00:04:48,998 --> 00:04:49,832
Aku baru ingat.

74
00:04:49,915 --> 00:04:54,795
Katanya dia putri aktris Jeong Nan-hee.

75
00:04:55,629 --> 00:04:58,549
Pantas dia cantik.

76
00:05:00,134 --> 00:05:02,428
Jadi, apa masalahnya? Dia salah apa?

77
00:05:02,511 --> 00:05:04,346
Itu menjjikkan.

78
00:05:04,847 --> 00:05:06,932
Hubungan dengan orang tua siswa.

79
00:05:07,016 --> 00:05:08,726
Astaga.

80
00:05:09,893 --> 00:05:12,646
Jangan beri tahu siapa pun soal itu.

81
00:05:13,230 --> 00:05:14,231
Mengerti?

82
00:05:15,691 --> 00:05:17,317
Berarti Kakak harus menang.

83
00:05:18,819 --> 00:05:21,822
Jika Han-gyul Jahat kalah,

84
00:05:21,905 --> 00:05:24,408
aku akan menuruti Kakak.

85
00:05:28,328 --> 00:05:29,204
Baiklah.

86
00:05:29,830 --> 00:05:31,999
Mari kita mulai
Festival Olahraga SMA Shinsu

87
00:05:32,082 --> 00:05:34,126
dengan lomba pertama.

88
00:05:34,209 --> 00:05:37,463
Lomba pertama adalah lari estafet.
Bukankah menyenangkan?

89
00:05:37,546 --> 00:05:40,132
Betul. Perhatikan atlet Tim Putih,
Oh Dong-pyo,

90
00:05:40,215 --> 00:05:41,633
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">pelari 100 m dalam 12 detik.</font></i>

91
00:05:41,717 --> 00:05:44,386
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Choi Se-jin dari Tim Biru,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">100 m dalam 15 detik.</font></i>

92
00:05:44,470 --> 00:05:46,597
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Lalu nenek Oh Dong-pyo, Yang Bok-hee,</font></i>

93
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:48,766
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">juga ikut sebagai pimpinan Tim Putih.</font></i>

94
00:05:48,849 --> 00:05:52,311
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Ada Sun Han-gyul,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">siswa terbaik sekolah kita,</font></i>

95
00:05:52,394 --> 00:05:55,147
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">juga Yoon Bom,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">guru etika yang sedang naik daun.</font></i>

96
00:05:55,230 --> 00:05:56,398
{\an8}TIM PUTIH

97
00:05:56,482 --> 00:05:58,275
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Barisan Tim Putih luar biasa.</font></i>

98
00:05:58,358 --> 00:06:00,110
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Tim Biru juga sama kuatnya.</font></i>

99
00:06:00,194 --> 00:06:02,696
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Hong Jung-pyo, guru sains</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">dan Direktur Akademik.</font></i>

100
00:06:02,780 --> 00:06:05,074
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kim Min-guk, tukang jahil SMA Shinsu,</font></i>

101
00:06:05,157 --> 00:06:07,868
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">dan ibunya, Seo Hye-suk,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">pengajar Bahasa Korea.</font></i>

102
00:06:07,951 --> 00:06:08,994
{\an8}TIM BIRU

103
00:06:09,078 --> 00:06:11,205
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kita hanya tahu pemenangnya di akhir.</font></i>

104
00:06:11,288 --> 00:06:13,874
Itulah mengapa tak menyerah hingga akhir

105
00:06:13,957 --> 00:06:15,459
bisa menjadi strategi kunci.

106
00:06:15,542 --> 00:06:16,460
Benar sekali.

107
00:06:43,112 --> 00:06:44,947
Apa ini?

108
00:06:45,030 --> 00:06:48,283
Kau pikir ini final Olimpiade?

109
00:06:48,367 --> 00:06:49,451
Kenapa?

110
00:06:49,535 --> 00:06:51,453
Karena terlalu keren, kau tak mengenali?

111
00:06:59,002 --> 00:07:01,797
Pelari estafet, majulah!

112
00:07:05,551 --> 00:07:06,718
Semangat.

113
00:07:07,469 --> 00:07:08,303
Kenapa?

114
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:13,267
Meski situasi berubah, janji kita tidak.

115
00:07:14,226 --> 00:07:15,185
Aku

116
00:07:15,811 --> 00:07:17,104
mengandalkan Paman.

117
00:07:18,647 --> 00:07:19,857
Han-gyul, soal itu…

118
00:07:19,940 --> 00:07:21,191
Astaga. Tunggu.

119
00:07:21,275 --> 00:07:26,238
Kakimu sakit karena menebang pohon.
Kenapa kemari?

120
00:07:26,321 --> 00:07:28,532
Biar aku yang jadi pimpinan orang tua.

121
00:07:28,615 --> 00:07:32,161
Cepat istirahat!

122
00:07:32,244 --> 00:07:33,078
Pergi!

123
00:07:33,162 --> 00:07:35,455
-Sebentar…
-Menyingkirlah dahulu.

124
00:07:35,539 --> 00:07:37,833
-Namun…
-Ayo, sudah dimulai.

125
00:07:38,333 --> 00:07:40,460
Bu Bom. Aku…

126
00:07:40,544 --> 00:07:41,545
-Hei.
-Ayolah.

127
00:07:41,628 --> 00:07:43,630
Apa aku salah dengar?

128
00:07:43,714 --> 00:07:46,049
-Pelari pertama…
-Nenek Dong-pyo berlari?

129
00:07:46,133 --> 00:07:47,551
-Ambil posisi!
-Semangat!

130
00:07:48,468 --> 00:07:49,344
Bu Bom.

131
00:07:49,970 --> 00:07:53,307
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">"Fiat justitia ruat caelum", </font></i>benar?

132
00:07:54,016 --> 00:07:55,517
Mari kita kerahkan segalanya.

133
00:07:55,601 --> 00:07:58,228
Kita akan melihat keadilan ditegakkan.

134
00:07:58,312 --> 00:07:59,521
Kita menonton saja.

135
00:08:00,189 --> 00:08:01,064
Ayo, Han-gyul!

136
00:08:01,148 --> 00:08:02,316
Tunggu aba-aba…

137
00:08:06,403 --> 00:08:10,073
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Pamannya… tak ikut serta?</font></i>

138
00:08:12,701 --> 00:08:13,535
Mulai!

139
00:08:13,619 --> 00:08:14,786
Yoon Bom agak terlambat.

140
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:15,996
Cepat!

141
00:08:16,580 --> 00:08:19,750
Wah, awal Hong Jung-pyo sangat baik.

142
00:08:19,833 --> 00:08:22,419
Dia tak mengalah sama sekali.

143
00:08:25,088 --> 00:08:26,006
Pakai lenganmu!

144
00:08:34,223 --> 00:08:36,016
Yoon Bom makin cepat.

145
00:08:36,850 --> 00:08:38,143
Cepat!

146
00:08:38,227 --> 00:08:39,728
Dia hampir membalap!

147
00:08:40,312 --> 00:08:43,732
Yoon Bom datang!

148
00:08:47,527 --> 00:08:48,820
Tidak.

149
00:08:48,904 --> 00:08:49,905
Lihat!

150
00:08:49,988 --> 00:08:50,948
Curang!

151
00:08:51,031 --> 00:08:53,283
Hong Jung-pyo, tak boleh begitu.

152
00:08:53,367 --> 00:08:54,243
Curang!

153
00:08:54,326 --> 00:08:58,372
Apa yang terjadi? Postur Yoon Bom salah.

154
00:08:58,455 --> 00:09:01,667
Hong Jung-pyo menjauh lagi.

155
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:03,001
Astaga!

156
00:09:04,628 --> 00:09:06,380
Yang benar saja!

157
00:09:06,463 --> 00:09:11,510
Itu dia. Seo Hye-suk
dan Yang Bok-hee dapat tongkatnya.

158
00:09:11,593 --> 00:09:12,803
Nenek Dong-pyo.

159
00:09:12,886 --> 00:09:14,012
-Nenek!
-Nenek!

160
00:09:14,096 --> 00:09:15,889
SUN HAN-GYUL
TERBAIK SEALAM SEMESTA

161
00:09:15,973 --> 00:09:16,807
-Nenek.
-Nenek!

162
00:09:16,890 --> 00:09:18,684
Apa ini? Nek!

163
00:09:20,143 --> 00:09:21,061
Astaga.

164
00:09:21,144 --> 00:09:22,688
Apa yang terjadi di sini?

165
00:09:22,771 --> 00:09:26,149
Apakah Yang Bok-hee
sungguh berlari sekuat tenaga?

166
00:09:26,233 --> 00:09:30,153
Akankah Tim Putih kembali kehilangan
kesempatan memimpin?

167
00:09:30,237 --> 00:09:32,781
Ayo! Lebih cepat!

168
00:09:33,615 --> 00:09:35,367
Bagaimana ini, Han-gyul Jahat?

169
00:09:35,450 --> 00:09:37,494
Kurasa aku akan lewati pita lebih dulu.

170
00:09:38,161 --> 00:09:39,788
-Kini pelari ketiga
-Mari.

171
00:09:39,871 --> 00:09:41,290
sedang bersiap.

172
00:09:41,373 --> 00:09:43,125
Han-gyul, cepat!

173
00:09:44,876 --> 00:09:45,836
Ayo!

174
00:09:46,461 --> 00:09:48,046
Nek, oper ke Han-gyul.

175
00:09:51,383 --> 00:09:52,342
Cepat!

176
00:09:52,426 --> 00:09:53,885
Han-gyul!

177
00:09:53,969 --> 00:09:55,470
-Cepat!
-Ayo!

178
00:09:55,554 --> 00:09:56,680
PEMENANG KETAMPANAN

179
00:09:56,763 --> 00:09:58,557
-Kenapa dia cepat sekali?
-Tunggu.

180
00:09:58,640 --> 00:10:01,101
-Sun Han-gyul!
-Sun Han-gyul!

181
00:10:01,184 --> 00:10:02,185
Apa ini?

182
00:10:02,269 --> 00:10:06,356
Sun Han-gyul mengejar Kim Min-guk.

183
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:07,941
Sun Han-gyul membuatku gila!

184
00:10:08,025 --> 00:10:09,735
Kau pemilik hatiku!

185
00:10:09,818 --> 00:10:11,653
Sun Han-gyul membuatku gila!

186
00:10:11,737 --> 00:10:13,447
Kau pemilik hatiku!

187
00:10:13,530 --> 00:10:15,032
Sun Han-gyul membuatku gila!

188
00:10:15,115 --> 00:10:16,575
Kau pemilik hatiku!

189
00:10:16,658 --> 00:10:19,328
Sun Han-gyul sungguh membuat kita gila.

190
00:10:19,411 --> 00:10:21,204
Dia tak mengampuni lawan.

191
00:10:21,288 --> 00:10:23,957
Akankah dia membalap?

192
00:10:24,666 --> 00:10:25,917
Dia membalap!

193
00:10:26,001 --> 00:10:29,087
-Sun Han-gyul memimpin!
-Dia memimpin!

194
00:10:30,422 --> 00:10:31,757
Semangat!

195
00:10:32,591 --> 00:10:33,633
Cepat!

196
00:10:34,176 --> 00:10:35,093
Han-gyul.

197
00:10:35,177 --> 00:10:36,178
Ini.

198
00:10:44,227 --> 00:10:46,480
Apa yang terjadi?

199
00:10:46,563 --> 00:10:49,733
Tongkatnya terbang!

200
00:10:58,033 --> 00:10:59,242
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kemarin, kau bertanya</font></i>

201
00:11:00,660 --> 00:11:04,039
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">apakah aku berniat baik atau jahat.</font></i>

202
00:11:05,374 --> 00:11:10,045
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Setelah Festival Olahraga berakhir,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">kau akan tahu jawabannya.</font></i>

203
00:11:15,842 --> 00:11:17,636
AYO, TIM BIRU! TIM BIRU
HAN-GYUL

204
00:11:53,839 --> 00:11:54,840
Hei.

205
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:57,175
Anjing itu…

206
00:11:57,259 --> 00:11:59,010
Ada-ada saja.

207
00:11:59,511 --> 00:12:01,221
-Cepat, Se-jin!
-Ayo!

208
00:12:01,304 --> 00:12:03,682
Anjing siapa itu?

209
00:12:05,016 --> 00:12:06,351
KAPTEN

210
00:12:06,935 --> 00:12:09,438
Lepas! Lepaskan!

211
00:12:09,521 --> 00:12:10,522
Lepaskan, Bodoh!

212
00:12:10,605 --> 00:12:12,232
Dong-pyo, sedang apa?

213
00:12:13,442 --> 00:12:14,568
Lepas.

214
00:12:15,652 --> 00:12:18,363
Lari, Dong-pyo! Cepat!

215
00:12:18,447 --> 00:12:20,740
Oh Dong-pyo akhirnya mendapat tongkat

216
00:12:20,824 --> 00:12:23,452
dan mengejar Choi Se-jin.

217
00:12:23,535 --> 00:12:25,454
Lebih cepat! Pakai lenganmu!

218
00:12:25,537 --> 00:12:28,290
Akan sulit mengejar Choi Se-jin.

219
00:12:28,373 --> 00:12:29,374
Semangat, Se-jin!

220
00:12:36,214 --> 00:12:37,424
Benar sekali.

221
00:12:37,507 --> 00:12:40,260
Choi Se-jin mencapai garis finis

222
00:12:40,343 --> 00:12:43,680
dan merebut kemenangan!

223
00:12:46,349 --> 00:12:48,602
Aku menang, Kak!

224
00:12:48,685 --> 00:12:50,812
Aku menghancurkan Han-gyul Jahat!

225
00:12:58,862 --> 00:13:00,238
Kerja bagus, Adikku.

226
00:13:05,994 --> 00:13:06,995
Han-gyul.

227
00:13:07,078 --> 00:13:09,206
Jika kau begitu, bagaimana menangkapnya?

228
00:13:09,289 --> 00:13:12,375
Begitu saja tak bisa tangkap?

229
00:13:12,459 --> 00:13:15,170
Saat latihan,
kusuruh perhatikan baik-baik.

230
00:13:15,253 --> 00:13:17,714
